{{Quote|No business can operate without an income. Governments have the luxury of taxation. We do not.|Opeli Mors|<ref name="The New Jedi Order: Edge of Victory II: Rebirth">''[[The New Jedi Order: Edge of Victory II: Rebirth]]''</ref>}}
The '''Jin'ri trade syndicate''' was a group of war profiteers formed after the fall of [[Duro/Legends|Duro]] to meet the demands of the refugees.

They sent [[Opeli Mors]] as their representative to a [[Yuuzhan Vong]] resistance meeting at [[Shelter]] station, offering their services in supplying troops and ships for a price. As an act of good faith and investment, a ship was loaned to the resistance with no charge.

